亚马逊的智能电视系列。然而，我们也看到其他电子产品也有大幅折扣，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23910368/amazon-october-prime-day-best-headphone-earbud-deals- 2023&quot;>;降噪耳塞&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23909229/amazon-october-prime-day-best-gaming-game-deals-2023&quot;>;游戏配件&lt;/a>;、&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23910515/amazon-october-prime-day-best-fitness-tracker-smartwatch-deals-2023&quot;>;智能手表&lt;/a>;、&lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23911169/october-amazon-prime-day-best-laptop-deals-2023&quot;>;笔记本电脑&lt;/a>;，以及 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/23906464/amazon-october-prime-day-best-smart-home-deals-device-google-alexa-2023&quot;>;各种智能家居配件&lt;/a>;（包括视频门铃）。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23903764/amazon-october-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2023&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23903764/amazon-october-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2023" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23903764/amazon-october-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2023</id><author><name>边缘员工</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-11T17:53:05-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-11T17:53:05-04:00</updated><title> T-Mobile 正在推动一些无限制客户购买价格更高的套餐</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;T-Mobile 标牌挂在店面&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ZXzkV-q9lGMwWvCbb9waN0nZCxQ=/0x0:5548x3699/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72746218/1636133771.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Anna Moneymaker / Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;tgiZIa&quot;>;从下周开始，T-运营商移动将把一些旧的无限制套餐的订户转移到新的（在某些情况下，更昂贵的）选项&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cnet.com/tech/mobile/t-mobile- is-forced-moving- those-on-old-plans-to-some-of-its-newer-ones-in-11月/&quot;>;已向 CNET 确认&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/em>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;0180aK&quot;>;根据文档，该计划将适用于 One、Simple Choice、Magenta 和 Magenta 55 Plus 计划的用户&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .reddit.com/r/tmobile/comments/174s0rx/forced_plan_migrations_coming_soon/&quot;>;发布在 Reddit&lt;/a>; 上。受影响的用户将通过“短信和电子邮件”收到通知，新计划将从 11 月的计费周期开始生效。客户看到的价格上涨将根据他们的计划而有所不同，但大多数人预计会上涨 &lt;a href=&quot;https://tmo.report/2023/10/breaking-t-mobile-will-force-customers-onto- newer-plans-unless-you-opt-out/&quot;>;每行 5 美元或 10 美元&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;n9r1BY&quot;>;T-Mobile 向 CNET 澄清，受影响的人&lt;em>;可以&lt;/em>;选择退出这一举措并继续执行原来的计划。为此，您需要拨打 T-Mobile 的客户服务支持热线。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;6YXpjo&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;reddit-embed-bq&quot; style=&quot;height:500px&quot; data-embed-created=&quot;2023-10-11T20:33:24Z&quot;>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/tmobile/comments/174s0rx/forced_plan_migrations_coming_soon/&quot;>;F...&lt; /a>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/11/23913290/t-mobile-automatic-plan-upgrade-customer-service -无限&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/11/23913290/t-mobile-automatic-plan-upgrade-customer-service-unlimited" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/11/23913290/t-mobile-automatic-plan-upgrade-customer-service-unlimited</id><author><name>陈莫妮卡</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-11T17:53:04-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-11T17:53:04-04:00</updated><title>黄金日最佳耳塞和耳机优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;木桌上 Bose QuietComfort Earbuds II 的俯视图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Qm7xnHofxxD20BvHVsg9UnH6pMs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72740020/DSCF9291_3.5.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;EI1aCv&quot;>;&lt;em>;亚马逊秋季 Prime Day 活动正在进行中。如需了解我们推荐的所有类别的更多优惠，请查看我们的&lt;/em>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/11/23912000/prime-day-best-deals-tech-earbuds -gaming-amazon-october&quot;>;&lt;em>;此处为完整综述&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>;。&lt;/